                <p style="padding:5px 0;font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;font-size: 14px;line-height:21px;font-style:italic;letter-spacing:-0.308px;margin-top:0">Join us for a night of cocktails, conversations, and networking on the sidelines of Money20/20 in Amsterdam. Spaces are limited. <a style="text-decoration: underline; color: #b61313 !important;" href="https://luma.com/bjihqfj5">RSVP here</a>.</p>

